headline: TRU Simulation announces delivery and acceptance of the Bell 505 Flight Training Device to Royal Jordanian Air Force
summary: TAMPA, Fla., November 13, 2025--TRU Simulation + Training Inc. announced delivery and acceptance of the Bell 505 Flight Training Device to the Royal Jordanian Air Force.
